## Inspiration

mvw is built with [Typer](https://github.com/Textualize/textual) + [iterfzf](https://github.com/dahlia/iterfzf) and inspired by:
- [fastfetch](https://github.com/fastfetch-cli/fastfetch) - Visual system information Display.

